methods.getTupleClassName:
Get the tuple class name for the supplied array of element classes.

:param classes: (java.lang.Class...) - The element classes
:return: (java.lang.String) The tuple class name
methods.getTupleImport:
Prepend the output package name to the supplied tuple class name.

:param className: (java.lang.String) - The tuple class name
:return: (java.lang.String) The full tuple class name for an import statement

text: Generator for a library of semi-opaque classes for tuple (ordered, multi-element) keys.
